ty and mass profiles. An appendix compares the\ndeprojected S\\'ersic profiles with those of the popular simple models from\nPlummer (1911), Jaffe (1983), Hernquist (1990), Navarro et al. (1996), and\nEinasto (1965).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jan 2020 17:33:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-03"}
