 consequences for both cosmic magnetogenesis and\naxionic dark matter in the Universe. Finally, the stringy RVM scenario\npresented here predicts quintessence-like dynamical dark energy for the current\nUniverse, which is compatible with the existing fitting analyses of such model\nagainst observations\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jan 2020 18:05:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Feb 2020 19:38:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-10"}
